<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Redemption Notification: RecCoins to Cash Conversion</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f7f7f7;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px 0;
        }
        .content h2 {
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #0073e6;
        }
        .content p {
            margin: 10px 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .details {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .details p {
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Redemption Notification</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Dear Accounts Team,</h2>
            <p>This is to inform you that a redemption request for RecCoins to cash has been processed by {{ name }}. Below are the details for your records:</p>
            <div class="details">
                <p><strong>Bank Name:</strong> {{bankName}}</p>
                <p><strong>IFSC Code:</strong> {{ifscCode}}</p>
                <p><strong>Account Number:</strong> {{accountNumber}}</p>
                <p><strong>Coins Redeemed:</strong> {{value}}</p>
                 <p><strong>Total Amount: </strong>INR {{totalValue}}/-</p>
            </div>
            <p>Please proceed with the transfer of the redeemed amount to the designated account as per our standard procedures.</p>
            <p>Thank you for your attention to this matter.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; Infoaptotechnologies</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
